title: #703 - Jordan Belfort
description:
Jordan Belfort, a salesman, motivational speaker, and author of two books including "The Wolf of Wall Street," which was adapted into a movie by Martin Scorsese and Leonardo DiCaprio, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
